      "writtenOn": "2018-06-06T20:16:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The max GLES version and EGLContext versions are different values, we should keep them separated. From my impression eglSetMaxGLESVersion determines the maximum version of EGLContext you can use. And the EGLContext version is the emulated version of the GLES context.\n\nWe would not want to change eglSetMaxGLESVersion that often. We can keep the global max GLES version set to 3 for the whole run, while each context has its own GLES version.",
